as per online search Unnamed groups like (?:js|css) are not supported, causing the build to fail.To fix the invalid header at index 1, update your vercel.json to use a path segment with the wildcard extension.How to FixReplace your regex source pattern with Vercel's supported path syntax:json{
  "source": "/(.*)\\.(js|css)",
  "headers": [
    {
      "key": "Cache-Control",
      "value": "public, max-age=31536000, immutable"
    }
  ]
}
Change it to the standard Vercel format utilizing a catch
